## 7. Latency Analysis

### How We Achieve < 1.5 Second Response Time

Each stage processes data **in parallel** (streaming), not sequentially:

```
Sequential (slow):
[===STT 300ms===] → [===LLM 800ms===] → [===TTS 500ms===] → [===Simli 300ms===]
Total: ~1.9 seconds ❌

Pipelined/Streaming (our approach):
[===STT 300ms===]
       [===LLM streaming===]
            [===TTS streaming===]
                 [===Simli streaming===]
Total perceived: ~1.0–1.4 seconds ✅
```

| Stage | Latency |
|-------|---------|
| Voice Activity Detection (Silero) | ~100ms |
| Deepgram STT (streaming) | ~200–300ms |
| GPT-4o-mini (streaming) | ~200–400ms |
| Cartesia TTS (streaming) | ~200ms |
| Simli avatar rendering | ~100–200ms |
| **Total (pipelined)** | **~1.0–1.4 seconds** |

