## 9. MVP Timeline Estimate

| Phase | Duration | Deliverable |
|-------|----------|-------------|
| Setup & Integration | 3–4 days | Pipecat pipeline + Simli + Deepgram + Cartesia working |
| Session Logic | 2–3 days | LangChain brain with script follow, reask, acknowledge |
| Backend API + Database | 2 days | FastAPI + MongoDB, session/message storage |
| Frontend | 2–3 days | Session page with avatar + doctor review page |
| Testing & Polish | 2 days | End-to-end testing, latency optimization |
| **Total** | **~11–14 days** | **Fully working MVP demo** |

